OL,7,Fspearheading the wider regeneration of
OL,8,Fthe Stephenson Quarter, before the
OL,9,Fcity council pulled the plug on that
OL,10,Fcontract in 2018 and subsequently
OL,11,Flaunched a joint venture with
OL,12,Fdevelopers PfPigloo for the remainder
OL,13,Fof the site.
